CLIENT (Frontend)
   ↓ gửi request (ví dụ GET /users)
JWT FILTER (check token)
   ↓ hợp lệ?
      yes → CONTROLLER
      no  → trả 401
CONTROLLER
   ↓ gọi SERVICE
SERVICE
   ↓ gọi REPOSITORY
REPOSITORY
   ↓ trả data
SERVICE
   ↓ xử lý (merge, validate…) → trả data
CONTROLLER
   ↓ trả JSON
